item.title: CVE-2023-39344|2024-10-04T19:37:11.953Z -- fobybus -- social-media-skeleton
item.description: social-media-skeleton is an uncompleted social media project. A SQL injection vulnerability in the project allows UNION based injections, which indirectly leads to remote code execution. Commit 3cabdd35c3d874608883c9eaf9bf69b2014d25c1 contains a fix for this issue.
